\v 5 Ngɨ́²ɨɨ' coon²¹ tsáa¹ tyani 'in jo cwii¹in Ña'ñʉ'¹ʉ' Jesucristo. Cwoo'¹³‑'oo' jmaa²aa' 'e sá² jmaa²aa'.
