\v 7 Joon 'in tsaru'¹u' Tíquico, 'in 'iin²¹²na'a, ijma'¹a 'naa' júu³ xiiala seen²¹na. Joon 'in Tíquico do nigauncoon'¹³o jna 'áai¹ joon coon²¹ caan²¹mo gacwoo²¹o'o júu³ tyʉ́² tya' Ña'ñʉ'¹ʉ'.
